{"tid":511804,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪上左年紀坐巴士都會咁","createTime":"2017-12-27T23:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T23:38:56.000Z","uid":154800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5e98146b465d8f529fa472661cbdd84d356d23","tid":511804,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T23:22:17.000Z","msg":"一上到車塞住個門口<br />\n係咁話你知唔知我等左好耐喇 有無搞錯你點揸車架<br />\n個司機膠都廢事比佢<br />\n條on9仲要話你做咩唔講野 啞左呀<br />\n仆街 企係佢後面想靜靜地坐個巴士都要出聲 你塞撚住個門口啊 咁矜貴咪學人坐巴士啦<br />\n佢仲要理直氣壯咁話我有入錢架 你學咩人插嘴 我唔係同緊你講野<br />\n心諗睇你個款都唔係第一日坐巴士啦 定其實上左年紀就咁中意撩交嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916a083c5a4a808ebef5e90a01cd90b4996afe41","tid":511804,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T23:23:15.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"8418ce5b4530428032f141e431540c973fd2da20","tid":511804,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T23:23:35.000Z","msg":"拍佢片貼上來"},{"pid":"2e1a0c6cb17af9eea355549aa136b950d9b9c66c","tid":511804,"uid":103011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T23:25:28.000Z","msg":"俾個幾蚊當自己貴客<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3f9d8ec311c6f6d64faef0e6e539a40330e833","tid":511804,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T23:38:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}